title: Volvo RTI Navigation DVD Europe 2008 Week 20 Disk 1
description:
Volvo RTI Navigation DVD Europe 2008 Made Week 20

This is the Disk 1 of the RTI Navigation DVD software from Volvo

This one includes the Maps of theses countrys:

Andorra, Austria, Belgium, France, Germany, Italy, Liechtenstein, Luxembourg, Monaco, Netherlands, San Marino, Switzerland, Vatican City State

This DVD will also update your Unit software so every time you start your car you&#039;ll have to press Enter to get rid of the annoying startup warning text :(

This one is ripped and tested using the software Imgburn and it&#039;s fully working
I&#039;ve burned it at 2,4x speed on a crappy DL DVD that my burner even can&#039;t find the media code :)
But it&#039;s working perfectly, no difference from the original DVD.

URL to info: http://www.volvocars.com/intl/salesandservices/maintenance/RTI/Pages/RTI_2008q2_DVD.aspx
